# Leavers Guide

When a team member leaves, follow this guide, and log completion in a ticket. 

## Line manager actions 

- Complete the [Leavers Checklist for Managers](https://intranet.justice.gov.uk/documents/2015/04/leavers-checklist-for-managers.docx)

## Revoking Access 

### Access to Cloud Optimisation and Accountability Team tools and services 

- Remove @justice.gov.uk email from Cloud Optimisation & Accountability Team MS Group, which revokes access to all MS platforms relating to it e.g. SharePoint, MS Teams. 
- Remove from [MoJ Github Organisation](https://github.com/ministryofjustice), [AP Github Organisation](https://github.com/orgs/moj-analytical-services/) and/or [ministryofjustice-test](https://github.com/ministryofjustice-test) **Note: Removal from GitHub will also remove access to other services that use this account for single sign-on i.e. AWS SSO, Sentry.io** 
